{"tid":640191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子山坡上自焚變焦屍","createTime":"2018-04-24T06:01:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T06:50:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"25e5c988d6f2559c8f48b737043bac5bdd4b5bbf","tid":640191,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:01:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180424/20370832?_ga=2.49033126.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180424%2F20370832%3F_ga%3D2.49033126.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=vHuKfvF7bamx%2B%2BckcQho84zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=d60b8e41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180424%2F20370832%3F_ga%3D2.49033126.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=e7c83196\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180424/20370832?_ga=2.49033126.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n男子山坡上自焚變焦屍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180424/large/24la7p05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180424%2Flarge%2F24la7p05.jpg&h=c49c4680&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警方到場調查，並設法了解死者身份。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名男子昨日被人發現全身燒焦，倒卧石硤尾大坑東邨對上一處山坡，救護員到場證實男子已死亡，並在其身旁發現易燃液體及打火機，警方初步懷疑他自焚死亡，身份則仍有待確認。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n遺易燃液及打火機<br />\n<br />\n死者疑為中國籍人士，中等身材，身高約1.65米，身旁有一副眼鏡、一隻銀色天梭錶及啡色涼鞋。<br />\n<br />\n昨晨6時許，有晨運客在大坑東邨開對山坡做運動時，發現一名男子身體多處燒焦倒卧梯間，立即報警。救護員趕至證實男子已死去一段時間，交由警方調查死因。警員在事主身旁發現一個盛有易燃液體的膠樽及一個打火機，其後派警犬上山嘗試搜索事主財物或證件，但未有進一步發現。警方懷疑男子自焚尋死，其後召仵工將屍體移送殮房，交由法醫確認死因。警方呼籲如有任何消息的市民，可致電36618887與調查人員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n■記者梁瑞帆  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n被指無㩒𨋢　女子遭金毛撼頭埋牆<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n茶果嶺再有三狗疑遇害"},{"pid":"23d51a4ca956977a7d3aed09cdfe4d36b713da89","tid":640191,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:04:02.000Z","msg":"被自殺姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d6a9963f3897027b8d01563452c730bfdababbc","tid":640191,"uid":34409,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:05:43.000Z","msg":"原來咁容易就被判斷係自焚架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4847c206dd2ebd6f06d74f02861d038bc57069d0","tid":640191,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:31:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b82b19c35703d9ead8bb5167731b307ffb82c0f4","tid":640191,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:36:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24eaa32dcccdd16b5ba2c2ae4e53b9d829c30a31","tid":640191,"uid":52282,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3d6a9963f3897027b8d01563452c730bfdababbc","tid":640191,"uid":34409,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:05:43.000Z","msg":"原來咁容易就被判斷係自焚架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:44:07.000Z","msg":"懷疑啫"},{"pid":"d4fb895b453feb6d6b6f8b00b63f5d1c5cf08bb5","tid":640191,"uid":124277,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:46:27.000Z","msg":"165cm ... 相信死因無可疑..."},{"pid":"c711db851843d793a2f5adad30068c8a5e0f63dc","tid":640191,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:48:54.000Z","msg":"中國籍人士成最大贏家"},{"pid":"45ee796bf98d692af997e3b0dfd412e697635a76","tid":640191,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:50:42.000Z","msg":"茶果嶺再有三狗疑遇害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}